<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. وَالْفِعْلِ لَيْسَ بِطَاعَةٍ حَتَّى يَجِي<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>أَمْرٌ بِهِ شَرْعًا إِلَى الإِنْسَانِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَالْعَامِلُونَ عَلَى وِفَاقِ الأَمْرِ لا<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>يَعْدُونَهُ بِالزَّيْدِ وَالنُّقْصَانِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَالْعَامِلُونَ بِمُقْتَضَى أَهْوَائِهِمْ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>هُمْ مُؤْثِرُونَ لِطَاعَةِ الشَّيْطَانِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>هَلْ مَا فَعَلْتُمْ جَاءَكُمْ أَمْرٌ بِهِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>مِنْ رَبِّكُمْ عَنْ صَاحِبِ التِّبْيَانِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>أَوْ هَلْ أَتَى مِنْ قُدْوَةٍ فِي الدِّينِ مِنْ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>صَحْبِ النَّبِي وَتَابِعِ الإِحْسَانِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَهُنَا لَكُمْ عِنْدِي نَصِيحَةُ مُخْلِصٍ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>لا يَمْتَرِي فِيمَا يَقُولُ اثْنَانِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>أَنْ تَأْخُذُوا بِالاحْتِيَاطِ لأَمْرِكُمْ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>قَبْلَ الْخُلُودِ بِمَوْقِدِ النِّيرَانِ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>إِنْ كَانَ مَا تَأْتُونَ لَيْسَ بِوَاجِبٍ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَالشِّرْكُ مَخْشِيٌّ لَدَى الإتْيَانِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>فَالابْتِعَادُ عَنْ الْمَخُوفِ مُقَدَّمٌ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>عَقْلاً عَلَى الأَقْدَامِ لِلإِنْسَانِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>خاتمة ونداء للعلماء<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>يَا مَعْشَرَ الْعُلَمَاءِ لَبُّوا دَعْوَةً<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>تُعْلِي مَقَامَكُوا عَلَى كِيوَانِ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>